Package com.aston.group.stationdefender.actors

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Actor
    Interface implemented by the Unit and Tower classes.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Alien
    Superclass for different Alien types.
    BossAlien
    Boss Alien displayed at the end of the level.
    CloseCombatAlien
    Fast Alien with slow, but high damage.
    CloseCombatWeapon
    Fast Alien with slow, but high damage.
    KamikazeAlien
    Alien with slow rate of fire and speed but a high damage.
    Mine
    Mine Alien with low range, low rate of fire and no speed (stays in one place) but has a high damage
    RapidFireAlien
    Fast Firing Alien with fast, but low damage.
    RapidFireWeapon
    RapidFireWeapon is a class that represents a RapidFireWeapon object that Humans (Unit) can arm themselves with and use to destroy Aliens.
    Tower
    Tower is the object which the Humans defend, and which the Aliens attack.
    Unit
    Abstract superclass inherited by Weapon and Alien subclasses.
    Weapon
    Weapon is a class that represents a weapon object that Humans (Unit) can arm themselves with and use to destroy Aliens
